sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(React SPA)
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API<br/>(Auth Check)
    participant Fastify as Fastify Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GenAI as Gen AI BFF<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant MaaSBFF as MaaS BFF<br/>8243/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack API<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant MaaSAPI as MaaS API<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Browser,LlamaStack: Flow 1: User Request to Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS (service cert)
    KRBAC->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Can user list projects?<br/>HTTPS/6443 · SA Token
    K8sAuth-->>KRBAC: Allowed
    KRBAC->>Fastify: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token<br/>x-auth-request-user<br/>x-auth-request-groups
    Fastify-->>KRBAC: Static assets (React SPA)
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTML/JS/CSS
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser,LlamaStack: Flow 2: Module Federation API Call (Gen AI → LlamaStack)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/responses<br/>HTTPS/443 · Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBAC->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAuth-->>KRBAC: Allowed
    KRBAC->>Fastify: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Fastify->>GenAI: HTTPS/8143<br/>x-forwarded-access-token passthrough<br/>TLS (service cert)
    GenAI->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>User can access LlamaStack service?<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>GenAI: Allowed
    GenAI->>MaaSBFF: HTTPS/8243 (inter-BFF)<br/>Token delegation
    MaaSBFF->>MaaSAPI: HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
    MaaSAPI-->>MaaSBFF: Token response
    MaaSBFF-->>GenAI: Delegated token
    GenAI->>LlamaStack: POST /v1/responses<br/>HTTPS · TLS 1.3<br/>Bearer Token (forwarded)
    LlamaStack-->>GenAI: AI Response
    GenAI-->>Fastify: JSON Response
    Fastify-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: AI Response

    Note over Browser,LlamaStack: Flow 3: Kubernetes Watch Stream (WebSocket)

    Browser->>Gateway: WSS Upgrade /wss/k8s/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: WSS/8443<br/>TLS (service cert)
    KRBAC->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAuth-->>KRBAC: Allowed
    KRBAC->>Fastify: WS/8080<br/>Token in WebSocket subprotocol<br/>(base64url-encoded)
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: WSS/6443<br/>User Token (from subprotocol)<br/>K8s Watch API
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: Stream: resource events
    Fastify-->>Browser: Stream: watch updates
